675f634ff132d4b47f2c1281.Description: A 9x19mm Parabellum FTX cartridge with a hollow-point bullet featuring a polymer-filled tip and a copper jacket, designed for self-defense and law enforcement use. The innovative FTX design ensures controlled expansion upon impact, providing exceptional stopping power and devastating wound channels while minimizing the risk of overpenetration.
